sentence.text: To our knowledge, no study investigates the association of genetic variant distributions of WW domain-containing oxidoreductase (negative regulation of Wnt signaling pathway) gene with development of invasive cancer, clinicopathologic variables and patient survival in uterine cervical cancer for Taiwanese women.
